  <description>
    <p>
      Much faster, more beautiful and more powerful.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Features come with Whatsapp web</li>
      <li>Icon in systray with different icon if there is new messages</li>
      <li>Customizable Systray icons</li>
      <li>System style (light and dark)</li>
      <li>Fullscreen mode</li>
      <li>Background running</li>
      <li>Spellchecker</li>
      <li>Drag and drop</li>
      <li>Work area notifications</li>
      <li>Personalized window decoration</li>
      <li>Shortcuts for the main options</li>
    </ul>
    <p>What doesn't include: Video calls and On-call calls</p>
  </description>

